sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant MM as ModelMesh Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>UDS/TCP gRPC
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant Puller as Storage Puller<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>MM: gRPC inference<br/>8033/TCP TLS (optional)<br/>mTLS (optional)
    MM->>Runtime: Forward to model server<br/>UDS or TCP gRPC<br/>pod-internal (no encryption)
    Runtime-->>MM: Prediction result
    MM-->>Client: gRPC response
    MM->>etcd: State sync<br/>2379/TCP gRPC TLS<br/>Username/password + client certs

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: REST Inference Request (RHOAI)
    Client->>OAuthProxy: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>OpenShift OAuth Bearer Token
    OAuthProxy->>RESTProxy: Forward (authenticated)<br/>8008/TCP HTTP<br/>pod-internal (no encryption)
    RESTProxy->>MM: Translate REST to gRPC<br/>8033/TCP gRPC TLS (optional)<br/>pod-internal
    MM->>Runtime: Forward to model server<br/>UDS or TCP gRPC<br/>pod-internal
    Runtime-->>MM: Prediction result
    MM-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
    RESTProxy-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP JSON response
    OAuthProxy-->>Client: HTTPS JSON response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Model Registration (Predictor Reconciliation)
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Predictor CR<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Predictor created/updated
    Controller->>MM: registerModel (SetVModel)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC TLS (optional)<br/>kube:// resolver
    MM->>etcd: Store model registration<br/>2379/TCP gRPC TLS<br/>Credentials from Secret
    MM->>Puller: Download model<br/>8086/TCP gRPC<br/>pod-internal
    Puller->>S3: Fetch model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Storage credentials
    S3-->>Puller: Model artifacts
    Puller-->>MM: Model cached locally
    MM->>Runtime: Load model
    Runtime-->>MM: Model loaded

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: etcd Event Streaming
    Controller->>etcd: EtcdRangeWatcher<br/>2379/TCP gRPC TLS mTLS<br/>Username/password + client certs
    etcd-->>Controller: Model state change events<br/>(vmodels/ and registry/ prefixes)
    Controller->>Controller: Update Predictor status
